  "notes": [
    "Pinned OCI SDK contract: LustreFileSystem lifecycle exposes CREATING, UPDATING, ACTIVE, INACTIVE, DELETING, DELETED, and FAILED. Repo-authored success is ACTIVE or INACTIVE, requeue covers CREATING and UPDATING, FAILED is terminal without requeue, and delete confirmation follows DELETING to DELETED.",
