    "ListLustreFileSystemsRequest filters by availabilityDomain, compartmentId, displayName, id, and lifecycleState and returns Items []LustreFileSystemSummary. Safe reusable matching is exact compartment_id plus availability_domain plus display_name, restricted to reusable ACTIVE, CREATING, UPDATING, or INACTIVE candidates; duplicate exact-name matches must fail instead of guessing."
